	<!WA20><a href=http://www.cs.duke.edu/~gadde/Java/tutorial/java/index.html#LANGUAGE>Writing Java Programs</a>,
	which contains the first three lessons shown on the index page
	for the trail.
	<li>
	<!WA21><a href=http://www.cs.duke.edu/~gadde/Java/tutorial/java/index.html#CORE>Using the Core Java Classes</a>,
	which contains the remaining six lessons.
	</ul>

    </td>
</tr>
